lead_paragraph: Jacob deGrom returned to the New York Mets on Saturday and says all is well with his infant son, Jaxon, following a scare the pitcher revealed was a breathing problem.

headline.print_headline: DeGrom Returns to Mets After Infant Son's Health Scare
